OL,3,CMore than half of teachers work at a
OL,4,Cschool where a child is homeless
OL,6,FMore than half of teachers in the
OL,7,FSouth West worked at a school in the
OL,8,Fpast year where a child is homeless, a
OL,9,Fsurvey has found.
OL,11,FThe survey, commissioned by charity
OL,12,FShelter found more than 175,000
OL,13,Fchildren in England are homeless in
OL,14,Ftemporary accommodation as of 2025.
