OL,6,F"Homelessness is taking an enormous
OL,7,Fphysical and emotional toll on
OL,8,Fchildren and young people, which is
OL,9,Fadversely affecting their education
OL,10,Fand ability to learn," he said.
OL,12,FHeadteachers' union the Association of
OL,13,FSchool and College Leaders (ASCL) has
OL,14,Fpreviously warned the burden placed on
OL,15,Fschools and teachers "has never been
OL,16,Fhigher", with schools running food
OL,17,Fbanks and supporting families with
OL,18,Fhousing while public services
OL,19,F"crumbled" around them.
